  "body": "For the old Optimism Kovan, our `dtl` stopped working. Although we have Kovan synced with latest state, we are getting:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":1665558869430,\"msg\":\"Cannot connect to L2, retrying 20/20\"}\r\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":1665558869430,\"msg\":\"Cannot connect to L2, shutting down\"}\r\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":1665558869430,\"msg\":\"Service is stopping...\"}\r\n{\"level\":30,\"time\":1665558869430,\"msg\":\"Service has stopped\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nProbably related is the fact that:\r\n```\r\nhttps://kovan-sequencer.optimism.io/\r\n```\r\nis not live anymore. What should we do to support old deprecated blocks from OP Kovan...?",
